                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, V</hi> 77.) I apprehended the prisoner—I told him he was charge with stealing a donkey—he told me he did not take the donkey off the common; but if he had been present when the other boy was tried, he would have given the young b—r more than he had got.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I met the boy on Kennington-common; he asked me to go with him; I went with him to Blackfriars-road, and he sold it there; he said, "It is one of Mr. Edwards's donkeys, but don't say anything about it;" he gave me half the money, and had half himself.</p>
